<div>
<p><strong>圣者杰胡提</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663869" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span>与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663869" alt="Ayers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ayers" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1856789); return false;">Ayers</a></span>，本文为<strong>群鸟之伍</strong>故事线的<strong>第八</strong>部分。</p>
<hr />
<div style="font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">
<p>这些作者的更多作品：<br />
<span style="font-size:130%;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/floppyphoenix" target="_blank">Lt Flops</a><br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/ayers-array" target="_blank">Ayers</a></span></p>
</div>
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></div>
<hr />
